z: Archive|accessdate=2010-06-01|work=|publisher=Mahasz|language=Hungarian}}</ref>\n\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.25em;font-size:90%;\"| [[MegaCharts|NLD]]<br><ref name=\"nld charts\">{{cite web|url=http://dutchcharts.nl/search.asp?search=nightwish&cat=a|title=Extended Search: Nightwish|accessdate=2010-06-01|publisher=Hung Medien &  hitparade.ch|work=Dutchcharts.nl|language=Dutch }}</ref>\n\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.25em;font-size:90%;\"| [[VG-lista|NOR]]<br><ref name=\"nor charts\">{{cite web|url=http://norwegiancharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Nightwish|title=Nightwish|accessdate=2010-06-01|publisher=Hung Medien|work=Norwegiancharts.com}}</ref>\n\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.25em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Sverigetopplistan|SWE]]<br><ref name=\"swe charts\">{{cite web|url=http://swedishcharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Nightwish|title=Nightwish|accessdate=2010-06-01|publisher=Hung Medien|work=Swedishcharts.com}}</ref>\n\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.25em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Swiss Hitparade|SWI]]<br><ref name=\"swi charts\">{{cite web|url=http://swisscharts.com/artist/Nightwish|title= Nightwish|publisher=Hung Medien|work=Swisscharts.com|accessdate=2011-01-17|language=German}}</ref>\n\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.25em;font-size:90%;\"| [[UK Albums Chart|UK]]<br><ref name=\"UK\">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/1312/nightwish/|title= Nightwish Chart History|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]}}</ref>\n\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.25em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Billboard 200|US]]<br><ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/312296/Nightwish/chart|title= Nightwish - Chart history|magazine=Billboard.com}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Angels Fall First]]''\n|\n* Released: November 1, 1997 <small>(FIN)</small>\n* Label: [[Spinefarm]]\n* Format: [[Compact disc|CD]], [[LP album|LP]], [[Compact Cassette|Cassette]]\n| 31 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 