nbawards\">{{cite web|url=http://www.nuclearblast.de/en/label/music/band/news/details/928393.70948.nightwish-receive-3-awards-from-nuclear.html|title=NIGHTWISH \u2013 Receive 3 Awards from Nuclear Blast!|publisher=Nuclearblast.de}}</ref>\n* US: 65,000+<ref>{{cite magazine|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20150321173437/http://hitsdailydouble.com/new_album_releases |archivedate= March 21, 2015 |url=http://hitsdailydouble.com/new_album_releases |title=Upcoming Releases |magazine=Hits Daily Double |publisher=HITS Digital Ventures }}</ref>\n* WW: 900,000+<ref name=\"wwsales\">{{cite web|url=https://yle.fi/uutiset/3-6672610|title=Nightwish n\u00e4yttely Kiteelle - b\u00e4ndin elokuva suositumpi maailmalla|publisher=Yle.fi|language=Finnish}}</ref>\n|\n* IFPI FIN: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"sales fin\"/>\n* IFPI GRE: Gold<ref name=\"nightwish.com\">{{cite web|url=http://nightwish.com/en/news|title=Latest News - Nightwish \u2013 The Official Website|publisher=Nightwish.com|access-date=2012-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007214546/http://nightwish.com/en/news|archive-date=2013-10-07|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n* IFPI SVK: Gold<ref name=\"nightwish.com\"/>\n* IFPI SWI: Gold<ref name=\"nightwish.com\"/>\n* BMVI: Gold<ref name=\"nightwish.com\"/>\n* ZPAV: Gold<ref name=\"sales pol\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Endless Forms Most Beautiful (album)|Endless Forms Most Beautiful]]''\n|\n* Released: March 27, 2015 <small>(EU)</small>\n* Label: Oily Empire/Sony Music, Nuclear Blast\n* Format: CD, LP, DD\n| 1 || 4 || 12 || 2 || 4 || 2 || 3 || 3 || 4 || 2 || 12 || 34\n|\n* FIN: 43,742+<ref name=\"sales fin\"/>\n* GER: 100,000+<ref name=\"efmb ger\"/>\n* US: 60,000+<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Vehicle-Spirit-Blu-Ray-Nightwish/dp/B01LXECCTF|title=Vehicle Of Spirit (With Blu-Ray) Box set|publisher=Amazon.co.uk}}</ref>\n|\n* IFPI FIN: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"sales fin\"/>\n* IFPI \u010cNS: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bravewords.com/news/night