cades (Nightwish album)|Decades]]''\n| \n* Released: March 9, 2018<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://loudwire.com/nightwish-decades-world-tour-2018/ |title=Nightwish Dig Into Past With Massive 'Decades: World Tour' |magazine=Loudwire |date=June 9, 2017 |accessdate=June 9, 2017 }}</ref>\n* Label: Nuclear Blast\n* Format: CD, LP\n| align=\"center\"| 1<br /><ref>http://ifpi.fi/tilastot/virallinen-lista/albumit/2018/11</ref>\n| align=\"center\"| 19<br /><ref>http://oe3.orf.at/charts/stories/oe3austriatop40longplay/</ref>\n| align=\"center\"| 5\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| align=\"center\"| 68\n| align=\"center\"| \u2014\n| align=\"center\"| 7\n| align=\"center\"| 62\n|\n|\n|-\n| colspan=\"100\" style=\"font-size:8pt; text-align: center\"| \"\u2014\" denotes releases that did not chart or was not released.\n|}\n\n==Singles==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"9\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Certifications\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| FIN<br /><ref name=\"fin charts\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| AUT<br /><ref name=\"aut charts\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| FRA<br /><ref name=\"fra charts\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| GER<br /><ref name=\"ger singles charts\">{{cite web|url=http://www.musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/Nightwish/?type=single|title=Charts \u2013 Nightwish/Singles|accessdate=2010-06-01|publisher=PhonoNet|work=Musicline.de|language=German|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508160720/http://www.musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/Nightwish/?type=single|archive-date=2016-05-08|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| HUN<br /><ref name=\"hun charts\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| NLD<